<i>noun</i>: 천시 [천ː시], 천대 [천ː대], 멸시 [멸씨], 능멸 [능멸], 경시 [경시] <i>verb</i>: 천시하다 [천ː시하다], 천대하다 [천ː대하다], 업신여기다 [업ː씬녀기다], 멸시하다 [멸씨하다], 능멸하다 [능멸하다], 경멸하다 [경멸하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>천시 [천ː시]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; disdain</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보거나 천하게 여김.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of looking down on someone or thinking of him/her as worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>천대 [천ː대]</dt><br>
<dd>disdain; contempt</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보거나 하찮게 여겨 함부로 다루거나 푸대접함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of belittling or looking down on someone or something, considering him/her or it worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>멸시 [멸씨]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; disdain</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 얕보거나 하찮게 여겨 무시함.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of looking down upon someone, or the belief that they are worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>능멸 [능멸]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; disdain; scorn</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 깔봄.</dd><br>
<dd>Belittling and looking down on someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경시 [경시]</dt><br>
<dd>contempt; negligence; disdain; slight</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상을 중요하게 보지 않고 하찮게 여김.</dd><br>
<dd>Treating someone or something with disdain.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>천시하다 [천ː시하다]</dt><br>
<dd>disdain; despise</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보거나 천하게 여기다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down on someone or think of him/her as worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>천대하다 [천ː대하다]</dt><br>
<dd>disdain; despise</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보거나 하찮게 여겨 함부로 다루거나 푸대접하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To belittle or look down on someone or something, considering him/her or it worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>업신여기다 [업ː씬녀기다]</dt><br>
<dd>disdain; belittle; underestimate</dd><br>
<dd>남을 낮추어 보거나 하찮게 여기다.</dd><br>
<dd>To belittle or look down on another person.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>멸시하다 [멸씨하다]</dt><br>
<dd>despise; disdain</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 얕보거나 하찮게 여겨 무시하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down upon someone or think that he/she is worthless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>능멸하다 [능멸하다]</dt><br>
<dd>scorn; disdain</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 깔보다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down on another person and belittle him/her.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경멸하다 [경멸하다]</dt><br>
<dd>disdain; despise; have contempt for someone</dd><br>
<dd>매우 싫어하거나 무시하는 듯한 태도로 낮추어 보다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down on someone with an attitude of extreme dislike or disdain.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>